    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom shine and no imperfections, while the interior is completely immaculate with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car drives as smoothly as the day it was manufactured. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in pristine, original state.",
